  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Through the Darkness find the Light!\nWhen The Legends of Dragons were first born, an age of darkness descended on the world of Lunar. Join the untried hero Jian and his friends on their journey to save Lunar from the powerful forces of evil.",
